<p>'I heard there was a chance when I wasn't on, but thankfully they didn't score. For one to fall our way is a very nice feeling.'</p>

<p>Mourinho told Sky Sports: 'Dier had to go, no other chance, he had to go. Maybe it's a normal thing when you are dehydrated, have nothing in your muscles.Â </p>

